  Select Cascade Mode
  Choose when Codex may delegate work to sub-agents.

› 1. Off (current)  Delegate only when you explicitly request sub-agents.
  2. On             Delegate proactively when parallel work would improve
                    speed or quality.

  Press enter to confirm or esc to go back
